ballot_measures.title: Citizenship Voting Requirement Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Amend the state constitution to state that only a citizen of the United States is eligible to vote. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Kansas 2026 ballot.

ballot_measures.number: Elections for Supreme Court Justices Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Elections for Supreme Court Justices Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Make the Kansas Supreme Court an elected office and to abolish the court's nominating commission. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Kansas 2026 ballot.
